  "text": "3.1.3.1 Long Text: Unlike general object detection, text usually come in varying aspect ratios. They have much larger height-width ratio, and thus general object detection framework would fail. Several methods have been proposed [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] , [CITATION_3] , specially designed to detect long text.",
